{"tid":1179183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：外國對修例有疑慮因不理解","createTime":"2019-05-31T02:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T03:25:51.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fb3c5d0e61ff1a382e6e651c70d05e9e3f3baeb9","tid":1179183,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190531_20190531-095343.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190531_20190531-095343.jpg&h=fc3f3dbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今早（31日）會見傳媒，就英國外相侯俊偉及加拿大外長方慧蘭聯合發表聲明關注《逃犯條例》修例或對《中英聯合聲明》保障的自由、權利有負面影響，她稱按其觀察，外國國家對修例有疑慮是因為對條例並不理解，若有機會，政府願意面對面逐一解說，相信能釋除很多疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n保安局長李家超就《逃犯條例》修訂再提新修訂，拋出6項建議；林鄭月娥稱，相關建議是回應社會訴求，否認傾斜商界，例如提高移交罪行門檻，適用於所有罪行，並非只是商業罪行，希望社會各界能理性務實討論。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，立法會保安事務委員會召開特別會議，討論《逃犯條例》修訂，政府會把握此平台解說，釋除疑慮。"},{"pid":"eb9b364a234aad46f6de18f32b76773ee1a419db","tid":1179183,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:39:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190531/s00001/1559268413267/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190531%2Fs00001%2F1559268413267%2F&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=007d0705\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190531%2Fs00001%2F1559268413267%2F&h=ea7763e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190531/s00001/1559268413267/</a>"},{"pid":"6ff662e4ca881ce7ef8585d3aaf70764bd1962f3","tid":1179183,"uid":130695,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:40:36.000Z","msg":"又錄音機"},{"pid":"13a765f12779b47ff665a6bc6de4cdda98596baf","tid":1179183,"uid":2772,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"